        },
        {
          "description": "Check gate \u2014 placeholder for workflows that delegate to GitHub branch protection (ADR-017 / #249). Carries no fields in v0.2; the merge-readiness signal lives in branch protection / rulesets, not in the spec.",
          "required": [
